{"tid":169750,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[牛扒撚] 平野一樣有好野","createTime":"2017-03-24T11:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T00:14:27.000Z","uid":31384,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"672e88715df46e98a1e031aceb4192c68d527bf3","tid":169750,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:16:42.000Z","msg":"用最簡單方整最完汁完味嘅牛扒<br />\n材料: 鹽， 黑椒碎 ，牛扒 。。無喇<br />\n<br />\n牛扒唔駛貴，六十幾蚊一樣可以好味<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wa039xoq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwa039xoq&h=2ac2f6cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用 鹽 黑椒碎兩邊醃一樣咁多，<br />\n我自己鐘意重口味，所以落勁多黑椒<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jtpuqg9x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjtpuqg9x&h=f0780370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒紅個鑊，落扒，記住唔好落任何油<br />\n同唔好㩒塊扒，煎完－邊先煎第二邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wldiegcj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwldiegcj&h=60798c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路煎會勁出煙，記住開大抽氣同通風<br />\n每邊只煎兩分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b6f8rjum\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb6f8rjum&h=ca04c2c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩分鐘反轉<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qi972bg4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqi972bg4&h=c5b95213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煎好上碟，等一至兩分鐘先切<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z62a4few\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz62a4few&h=b4bbbf91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開刀!<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lc15bu8v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flc15bu8v&h=f85cfd4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/e7x2h9po\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fe7x2h9po&h=d262c77d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70012bed5817e19c576affbb5e78f0d1a419657d","tid":169750,"uid":28677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387ff3c469cea7dd1ac7c6bdfaed46db96c63ac4","tid":169750,"uid":34596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:20:10.000Z","msg":"煎成咁我多數伶去餵狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9558c19023e763ccc32e105952ce543e2d9a6d32","tid":169750,"uid":12720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:20:41.000Z","msg":"幾時生癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5b7b1553162b5eaabab669e4d2adfc42144f57","tid":169750,"uid":68079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:21:16.000Z","msg":"太多黑椒<br />\n唔夠油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e103dc4d047979945425178ac24bb87f060dc24d","tid":169750,"uid":68505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:21:56.000Z","msg":"用最大火?"},{"pid":"d7a88943ff83c35970e7cd9bf60c1e1fcb17a4cd","tid":169750,"uid":19322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69Rc450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69Rc450.jpg&h=1f439c15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"889ab0b9dee139cac47a54783a05c6e07fdca360","tid":169750,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"戇鳩"},{"pid":"518165a01151a62ca351ea3a1847563df5c9ac81","tid":169750,"uid":59519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"4/10<br />\n<br />\nwrong pan, not enough oil<br />\nburnt black pepper<br />\nno butter"},{"pid":"b5fa114af4ee4d2f6eed08466bc70583db27d9e3","tid":169750,"uid":66171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"oh fuck me, <br />\n<br />\n<br